  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7966724">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7966724/" class="title-link">姑娘，30岁也可以绚丽突围</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7966724"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48047254/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u48047254-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48047254/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">慕夏CC</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-07-06"
      class="main-meta">2016-07-06 19:20:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7966724_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  刘晓庆曾说：“中国女人放弃自己太早了。”国内大都数30岁女人，应该过着结婚、相夫教子的生活，外加一份可有可无的工作，可能早已忘了什么叫精进自己。但总有人是“异类”，是引领社会前进的佼佼者，范海涛就是其中一员。  她的作品《就要一场绚丽突围:30岁后去留学》，这本书...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
